Precious Onyewuchi is a Technical Writer, Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI) advocate, and Open Source Educator with extensive experience in building and nurturing communities.
Her work in educating others about open source has made significant impact globally.
In her spare time, she hosts “The Open Source Education Podcast,” where she continues to share her expertise and passion for open-source technology.
